title: Cars of the future - expectations
summary: This grouped bar chart represents 7 different Races on X-axis for 2 groups I mostly agree, and I totally agree. On the Y-axis it shows their corresponding SOME LABEL.

Race Maximal safety had the maximum SOME LABEL among all 2 groups, and it was for I totally agree. The minimum SOME LABEL was observed in Race Driving enjoyment -Driving should be fun for I mostly agree.
In Race Maximal safety, I totally agree had the maximum SOME LABEL and it saw the lowest in Race Driving enjoyment -Driving should be fun out of all 7 Races.
The maximum SOME LABEL for I totally agree that was found in Race Maximal safety was 18.82 times larger than the minimum SOME LABEL observed in Race Driving enjoyment -Driving should be fun.
